- "That would be too easy."
- That'd be too easy.

38:52.797 --> 38:54.231
- "Watch this."
- Watch this.

38:54.264 --> 38:55.932
- Now you're going to cut
a little deeper.

38:55.965 --> 38:58.501
Cut a little deeper, like
two-thirds of the way down.

38:58.536 --> 39:00.237
- Two-thirds. Okay.

39:00.271 --> 39:02.072
- Now turn it over
just like you did before.

39:02.106 --> 39:03.507
Put it right back
down there and say,

39:03.541 --> 39:04.641
"Three of hearts.
Is that your card?"

39:04.675 --> 39:06.643
- Three of hearts.
Is that your card?

39:06.677 --> 39:09.112
Aw. That would be way too easy.
[laughter]

39:09.146 --> 39:11.449
- Way too easy, way too easy.
