Just spread them out.

39:20.724 --> 39:25.730
Now, take all the face-up
cards.

39:25.762 --> 39:27.797
You got to throw them down
over there with disdain

39:27.831 --> 39:29.132
and say, "none of them!"

39:29.166 --> 39:31.835
- None of them!
- Oh, your disdain is good.

