- [growling]
Yeah.

39:33.403 --> 39:34.672
- Now, get the card you cut
through, that card right there.

39:34.704 --> 39:35.940
Slide it over here.
Okay.

39:35.972 --> 39:38.175
Now take all those cards,
gather those cards,

39:38.208 --> 39:41.277
and then throw them down
with disdain and say,

39:41.311 --> 39:42.480
"None of them!"

39:42.512 --> 39:44.014
- None of them!
