39:44.047 --> 39:46.951
- Boy, your disdain--you got
a lot of hate there, don't you?

39:46.983 --> 39:48.219
- I'm so excited.

39:48.251 --> 39:49.452
- So there's one card left.
Don't look at--

39:49.487 --> 39:50.820
- I guess your energy
is very contagious.

